data.description: Don't miss this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in Center!  Multi level with kitchen, sunken living room and dining room on main level.  Upper level has 3 bedrooms and a bath with a jacuzzi tub!  Lower level has access to the garage, a very large family room and 3/4 bathroom.  The basement has a non-conforming bedroom, mechanical room and large storage room!  The private backyard has a patio, playhouse and shed!  Call your favorite agent today for a private showing!
